item.title: CVE-2021-24747|2024-08-03T19:42:16.686Z -- unknown -- seo%20booster
item.description: The SEO Booster WordPress plugin before 3.8 allows for authenticated SQL injection via the "fn_my_ajaxified_dataloader_ajax" AJAX request as the $_REQUEST['order'][0]['dir'] parameter is not properly escaped leading to blind and error-based SQL injections.
